            What is the best way to remove the tape?

                How customer reviews and ratings work

                Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

                To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

                Easy to Use:
                The application process is straightforward, and the tape is customizable to suit various breast sizes and shapes. You can cut the tape to fit your unique needs, making it incredibly versatile.

                Nipple Covers:
                The kit also includes nipple covers, an added bonus that provides an extra layer of protection and comfort. These are especially useful for those more revealing outfits where you don't want any accidental slips or exposure.

                Hypoallergenic:
                One of the best features of this kit is that the tape and nipple covers are hypoallergenic, reducing the risk of skin irritation. This is a crucial factor for anyone with sensitive skin who may be hesitant about using adhesive products.

                Water-Resistant:
                The tape is water-resistant, meaning you can wear it confidently to pool parties or while dancing the night away without worrying about it coming loose.

                Long-Lasting:
                The adhesive is strong enough to last all day (or night), so you dont have to carry an emergency roll of tape in your purse. It holds up well, giving you peace of mind to enjoy your event fully.

                4.0 out of 5 stars Awesome! Will need a good amount to be able to lift in all the right areas
                Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2022
                Color: BeigeVerified Purchase
                Works great but need a lot for it to really work for a bigger bust! It doesnt come off with movement or sweat but I definitely recommend having some sort of nipple covering because taking the tape off of the skin directly was pretty painful but that is an easy fix! You really want to make sure your placement is where you want it the first time because every time you remove it, it loses its adhesive. Although you may need a lot to get the job done, it does come with quite a bit of tape that will definitely let you use it for multiple occasions! Make sure when you apply it try to peel off the backing only where you want to start it on your body and then continue to peel it off as you go because it is easy to accidentally stick the tape to itself if you arent careful. Also I found it helpful to try to hold it up to your body to see the length you will want it beforehand to avoid wasting extra tape and use good scissors! ALSO! It is not see through at all with any of the thin and light colored clothing Ive used it with! However, with tighter clothing, as a larger busted woman, sometimes if I did it a little too tight or not enough tape, you could kind of see the indentations but I think it just takes a little bit of practice to know the best way to tape it for each outfit! Overall I am really really happy with the product and have been able to wear backless and strapless clothing that I literally have never been able to wear until now! And absolutely works for lifting and providing support. It comes with a little guide on the back of the box that shows you the best placement for different outfits and it definitely helps! I have always struggled with bras and feeling comfortable in clothing I really like but doesnt work for my chest so this has 100% changed the game for me and literally changed my confidence in how I feel in my clothing!
